{"id":571732,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/【立此存照】习特会：微博禁评特朗普访华、经/","date":"2017-11-09T10:40:06Z","modified":"2017-11-09T14:00:27Z","title":"【立此存照】习特会：微博禁评特朗普访华、“经贸大单”","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】毫不意外地，与特朗普访华相关微博会受到新浪的系统性审查。但这些审查似乎只是单纯地建立在关键词上的，与微博的具体内容无关</strong>，甚至只是转发了“90亿美元大单”的川粉的微博也会被删。截至发稿时，微博的重点审查对象为“90亿美元大单”和“2535亿大单”相关内容。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_571733\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-571733\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"336\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制1.jpg 1390w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制1-300x183.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制1-768x469.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制1-1024x625.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制1-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_571734\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-571734\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制2.jpg 1216w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制2-300x184.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制2-768x470.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制2-1024x627.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制2-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_571735\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-571735\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"490\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制3.jpg 1218w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制3-300x267.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制3-768x685.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/限制3-1024x913.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">川粉也被删；微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>与此同时，强制关闭评论是另一个在微博上常见的审查手段。与删除微博类似，审查者似乎只是单纯地设置了一些关键词，而相关微博的具体内容并不重要。</strong>除粉丝数极少的用户外，所有其他微博账号似乎都会在触发关键词后，被系统自动关闭评论。</p>\n<p><strong>以下为部分非认证用户（粉丝&gt;300）的微博截图示例：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_571744\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/无认证9.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-571744\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/无认证9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"343\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/无认证9.jpg 1214w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/无认证9-300x187.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/无认证9-768x478.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/无认证9-1024x638.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">非认证用户微博截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_571737\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/无认证7.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-571737\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/无认证7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"410\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/无认证7.jpg 974w, https://chinadigitaltimes.ne